author: geirm
msg: Tests to see if we can do a change of data object in the Context and remerge a template.
Note that this is not a trivial change, such as a different string, but altogether
something more evil, like switching between a j.u.Vector and an Object array.
This is what happens when multiple threads are using the same template with different
data objects in the template, or a single thread is repeatedly merging() with different
data objects. No one ran across it, yet, but we could, and eventually would.
